      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cider vinegar</strong> and <strong>mayo</strong> to the bowl with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and stir it all together – this is your<strong> slaw</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>chilli relish </strong>with 10ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[15ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[20ml] </span>water<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>chilli dip</strong></p>",
